property_description: Lifestyle - Occupying an Eastern position in this sought after security building, the apartment offers an inviting haven of light and space in an ultra-convenient locale. Provides convenient access to the newly built Coles & Aldi supermarkets. Short stroll to Supa Centa and the Golf Course. Accommodation - Beautifully presented and showcasing high quality finishes throughout, this generously proportioned retreat is perfectly appointed for easy living. Spacious open plan living area, while the double bedroom offers ample wardrobe space. There is also an internal laundry. Features - This fully air conditioned apartment is beautifully equipped to facilitate a comfortable yet stylish city fringe lifestyle. Bedroom has built-ins, while the gourmet gas kitchen is fitted with stone benches and stainless steel appliances including gas cooking. There is also an internal laundry plus intercom entry and lift access. Quality timber flooring throughout.

property_headline: STYLISH NORTH FACING TWO BEDROOM RESIDENCE IN RESORT STYLE COMPLEX
property_description: Available: 23 May 2025 Initial Lease Period: 12 months Inspect: Saturday, 10th of May 2025, 01:50 PM to 2:05 PM Privately situated on the top floor of Rosebery's award winning 'Metro Village' complex, this stylishly updated two bedroom residence enjoys a generous split-level floor plan with sun-drenched interiors & leafy northerly outlooks capturing city skyline views. Showcasing an executive city fringe lifestyle & boasting resort-style facilities with tranquil landscaped gardens & sparkling lap pool, this executive apartment will enjoy a brand new air conditioning system & is conveniently situated just moments to buzzing local cafes, vibrant bars & award-winning eateries, nearby shops including an IGA supermarket on the ground level, an array of surrounding leafy parks with bus stop on the doorstep & just a short stroll to Green Square Station. - Generous open plan living space with soaring ceilings seamlessly flows out onto the sun-drenched entertainer's terrace with leafy northerly aspects - Sleek gourmet gas kitchen with stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances & splashback as well as an abundance of cupboard space - Large loft-style master bedroom with mirrored built robes, ensuite bathroom with bathtub & uninterrupted northerly views across the city skyline - Good size second bedroom on the lower level enjoys private access out onto a second rear balcony - Fresh main bathroom tiled floor to ceiling with stylish stone countertops, combined shower/bathtub & mirrored vanity with storage - Internal laundry with separate wash basin & clothes dryer included - Ceiling fans with lights installed in both bedrooms & stylish pendant above the living area - Foxtel connection ready - New reverse cycle air conditioning installed both levels To register your interest in this property please click the 'Email Agent' button. Please contact Alistair at CPS Property on 0488 556 634 for more information.
